{"tid":2190703,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人發過夢中夢","createTime":"2020-09-06T02:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T15:34:39.000Z","uid":183177,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"5fd22e4dadc85eb235396f656df25288d78de2c9","tid":2190703,"uid":183177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:26:13.000Z","msg":"今日訓晏教個陣發咗個夢<br />\n夢見自己醒咗但有種力壓住心口<br />\n係咁大嗌都冇人幫手<br />\n不停爭扎大叫 終於郁到以為自己起咗身<br />\n同男朋友講話我發咗個夢好恐怖<br />\n本身都正正常常<br />\n點知我男朋友突然鏈住我條頸大力壓住我心口<br />\n我係咁問佢做咩咁做<br />\n再爭扎發現原來我仲係發緊夢<br />\n再以為自己起咗身<br />\n想攞起電話check下究竟點解會咁<br />\n之後又有野撳住自己 郁唔到以為自己就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後終於醒到 <br />\n見到男朋友仲訓緊以為仲係夢<br />\n嚇到我即刻拍醒佢大叫<br />\n佢都嚇醒埋<br />\n所有都好真<br />\n真係好恐怖 好似瀕死咗3次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇有試過咁？知唔知咁樣係暗示啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c771a5186a18feacd1d710c5b70391abe74cb35e","tid":2190703,"uid":343361,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:28:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f0b26cf85f438a5df6a468aab9235d36c0eadd4","tid":2190703,"uid":160348,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:28:43.000Z","msg":"成日都係夢中夢㗎啦。醒咗，點知仲係發緊夢<br />\n<br />\n有時有啲夢好似會echo返個夢初段嘅嘢咁㖭，懶有舖排咁"},{"pid":"6c03a96bcf287cc3a79f4b01ed32848cf4e026a8","tid":2190703,"uid":196924,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:32:39.000Z","msg":"我係你爸爸搵嚟訓練你對抗夢中夢嘅<br />\n可能你已經唔記得<br />\n但係你必須認清<br />\n你而家仲係發緊夢<br />\n快啲醒呀!"},{"pid":"f518a51864b889a8ad1056827ad73f82e686b422","tid":2190703,"uid":183177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c771a5186a18feacd1d710c5b70391abe74cb35e","tid":2190703,"uid":343361,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:28:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:32:44.000Z","msg":"但有冇識過抖唔到氣"},{"pid":"568ccd29cefe554b5a3b9e617a9d758b7033fc56","tid":2190703,"uid":183177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f0b26cf85f438a5df6a468aab9235d36c0eadd4","tid":2190703,"uid":160348,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:28:43.000Z","msg":"成日都係夢中夢㗎啦。醒咗，點知仲係發緊夢<br />\n<br />\n有時有啲夢好似會echo返個夢初段嘅嘢咁㖭，懶有舖排咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:33:39.000Z","msg":"係咁loop搞到我對現實有懷疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家好驚訓教"},{"pid":"2fbdd0f9b4f5510b2d9fd6e088eae5909c76ceaa","tid":2190703,"uid":320293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:34:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f63cd65fa2102e2ddfe199372b3a9de1882f14d6","tid":2190703,"uid":119080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:34:23.000Z","msg":"Inception<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a2f2c9e9e0fb36c5bda0133ad64f4498322d712","tid":2190703,"uid":183177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fbdd0f9b4f5510b2d9fd6e088eae5909c76ceaa","tid":2190703,"uid":320293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:34:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:36:24.000Z","msg":"我諗緊如果上唔到會唔會猝死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a9b6b3255bad806e810ba1c4bcf7832b87de0c","tid":2190703,"uid":339751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:42:32.000Z","msg":"以前係課室上堂訓覺<br />\n成日都會發夢中夢<br />\n下下都係驚醒咁樣訓醒咗<br />\n但疫情無返學之後就無發過了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c86f04275ba56a46a341e1e4efcb5ade60a472","tid":2190703,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f63cd65fa2102e2ddfe199372b3a9de1882f14d6","tid":2190703,"uid":119080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:34:23.000Z","msg":"Inception<img